properties.stmtText:
SUB-2000-PROCESS .
 
MOVE 0 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE LOW-VALUES TO FAKER-INFO-OCCS IN L-PARAMETER

SUB-9010-ADDRESS .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-ADDRESS' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-ADDRESS

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE W-TABLE-1 TO FAKER-TABLE IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

SUB-2200-SEPARATE-FIELDS .
 
MOVE 1 TO W-POINTER
UNSTRING FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER DELIMITED '\n' INTO FAKER-ADDRESS-STREET IN L-PARAMETER POINTER W-POINTER
UNSTRING FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER DELIMITED ', ' INTO FAKER-ADDRESS-CITY IN L-PARAMETER POINTER W-POINTER
UNSTRING FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER DELIMITED ' ' INTO FAKER-ADDRESS-STATE IN L-PARAMETER FAKER-ADDRESS-POSTCODE IN L-PARAMETER POINTER W-POINTER

MOVE W-FAKER-FORMAT TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT
MOVE 1 TO W-SUB-1
PERFORM SUB-2110-RECURSE-FORMATS THRU SUB-2110-EXIT UNTIL W-SUB-1 > LENGTH OF W-RECURSED-FORMAT OR NOT FAKER-RESPONSE-GOOD IN L-PARAMETER

MOVE SPACES TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE 1 TO W-SUB-1 W-SUB-2
PERFORM SUB-2120-PROCESS-FORMATS THRU SUB-2120-EXIT UNTIL W-SUB-1 > LENGTH OF W-RECURSED-FORMAT OR W-SUB-2 > LENGTH OF FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER OR W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1 : ) = SPACES

ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
UNSTRING W-RECURSED-FORMAT DELIMITED W-FORMAT-END INTO W-FORMAT-ENTRY POINTER W-SUB-1
STRING W-FAKER-RESULT DELIMITED '  ' INTO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER POINTER W-SUB-2

SUB-9020-BUILDING-NO .
 
MOVE 'BUILDING-NUMBER-FORMATS' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF BUILDING-NUMBER-FORMATS

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE W-TABLE-1 TO FAKER-TABLE IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9710-FIND-FORMAT THRU SUB-9710-EXIT VARYING L-F-DX-1 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-F-DX-1 > L-FORMAT-ENTRY-CNT-1

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE W-TABLE-2 TO FAKER-TABLE IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9720-FIND-FORMAT THRU SUB-9720-EXIT VARYING L-F-DX-2 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-F-DX-2 > L-FORMAT-ENTRY-CNT-2
MOVE 'Random format not found' TO W-FAKER-FORMAT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-F-DX-2
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 'Random format not found' TO W-FAKER-FORMAT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-F-DX-1
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

COMPUTE W-RANDOM-SUB = FAKRAND-RANDOM-NO * L-ADDRESS-ENTRY-CNT-1 + 1
MOVE W-RANDOM-SUB TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX ) W-FOUND-DX FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

COMPUTE W-POSTCODE = ( FAKRAND-RANDOM-NO * ( STATE-POSTCODE-MAX ( SP-DX ) - STATE-POSTCODE-MIN ( SP-DX ) ) ) + STATE-POSTCODE-MIN ( SP-DX ) + 1
COMPUTE W-RANDOM-SUB = FAKRAND-RANDOM-NO * POSTCODE-FORMAT-CNT + 1
MOVE L-ADDRESS-ENTRY-1 ( W-FOUND-DX ) ( 1 : 3 ) TO W-FAKER-RESULT ( 1 : 3 )
MOVE POSTCODE-FORMAT ( W-RANDOM-SUB ) TO W-FAKER-RESULT ( 4 : )
MOVE W-POSTCODE TO W-FAKER-RESULT ( 4 : 5 )

MOVE 0 TO W-DIGIT-CNT
INSPECT W-FAKER-RESULT TALLYING W-DIGIT-CNT FOR ALL W-HASH W-PERCENT
PERFORM SUB-9810-REPLACE-DIGIT THRU SUB-9810-EXIT VARYING W-SUB-D FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-SUB-D > LENGTH OF W-FAKER-RESULT
IF W-FAKER-RESULT ( W-SUB-D : 1 ) NOT = W-HASH AND W-PERCENT
MOVE W-FAKER-RESULT TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER

STRING W-FAKER-FORMAT DELIMITED '  ' INTO W-RECURSED-FORMAT POINTER W-SUB-1-SAVE
MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT-REST TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1-SAVE : )
MOVE FAKER-RESULT IN W-FAKER-PARAMETER TO W-FAKER-RESULT

SUB-9030-CITY .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-CITY' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-CITY

SUB-9040-CITY-PREFIX .
 
MOVE 'CITY-PREFIXES' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF CITY-PREFIXES

SUB-9050-CITY-SUFFIX .
 
MOVE 'CITY-SUFFIXES' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF CITY-SUFFIXES

SUB-9060-MILITARY-APO .
 
MOVE 'MILITARY-APO-FORMATS' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF MILITARY-APO-FORMATS

SUB-9070-MILITARY-DPO .
 
MOVE 'MILITARY-DPO-FORMATS' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF MILITARY-DPO-FORMATS

SUB-9080-MILITARY-SHIP-PREFIX .
 
MOVE 'MILITARY-SHIP-PREFIXES' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF MILITARY-SHIP-PREFIXES

SUB-9090-MILITARY-STATE-ABBR .
 
MOVE 'MILITARY-STATES-ABBR' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF MILITARY-STATES-ABBR

SUB-9100-POSTCODE .
 
MOVE 'POSTCODE-FORMATS' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF POSTCODE-FORMATS

SUB-9110-SECONDARY-ADDRESS .
 
MOVE 'SECONDARY-ADDRESS-FORMATS' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF SECONDARY-ADDRESS-FORMATS

SUB-9130-STATE-ABBR .
 
MOVE 'STATES-ABBR' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF STATES-ABBR

SUB-9140-STATE-POSTCODE .
 
MOVE 'STATES-POSTCODE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF STATES-POSTCODE

SUB-9150-STREET-ADDRESS .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-STREET-ADDR' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-STREET-ADDR

SUB-9160-STREET-NAME .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-STREET-NAME' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-STREET-NAME

SUB-9170-STREET-SUFFIX .
 
MOVE 'STREET-SUFFIXES' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF STREET-SUFFIXES

SUB-9190-FIRST-NAME .
 
MOVE 'FIRST-NAME' TO W-TABLE-1
SET PERSON-FIRST-NAME IN W-FAKER-PARAMETER TO TRUE
CALL W-FAKPERS-PROG USING W-FAKER-PARAMETER

SUB-9200-LAST-NAME .
 
MOVE 'LAST-NAME' TO W-TABLE-1
SET PERSON-LAST-NAME IN W-FAKER-PARAMETER TO TRUE
CALL W-FAKPERS-PROG USING W-FAKER-PARAMETER

MOVE SPACES TO W-TABLE-1
SET FAKER-UNKNOWN-FORMAT IN L-PARAMETER TO TRUE
STRING 'Unknown FAKADDR format "' W-FORMAT-ENTRY '"' DELIMITED SIZE INTO FAKER-RESPONSE-MSG IN L-PARAMETER
GO TO SUB-9000-EXIT

MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT-CHAR ( W-SUB-1 ) TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER ( W-SUB-2 : 1 )
ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1 W-SUB-2

ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
GO TO SUB-2110-EXIT

MOVE W-SUB-1 TO W-SUB-1-SAVE
ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
UNSTRING W-RECURSED-FORMAT DELIMITED W-FORMAT-END INTO W-FORMAT-ENTRY POINTER W-SUB-1

MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1 : ) TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT-REST
MOVE W-SUB-1-SAVE TO W-SUB-1

SUB-9120-STATE .
 
MOVE 'STATES' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF STATES

SUB-9180-TERRITORY-ABBR .
 
MOVE 'TERRITORIES-ABBR' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-ADDRESS-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF TERRITORIES-ABBR

SET FAKER-UNKNOWN-FUNCTION IN L-PARAMETER TO TRUE
STRING 'Unknown FAKADDR function "' FAKER-PROVIDER-FUNCTION IN L-PARAMETER '"' DELIMITED SIZE INTO FAKER-RESPONSE-MSG IN L-PARAMETER
GO TO SUB-2000-EXIT

SET W-NOT-FIRST-CALL TO TRUE
MOVE FUNCTION WHEN-COMPILED TO W-COMPILED-DATE
DISPLAY 'FAKADDR  compiled on ' W-COMPILED-DATE-YYYY '/' W-COMPILED-DATE-MM '/' W-COMPILED-DATE-DD ' at ' W-COMPILED-TIME-HH ':' W-COMPILED-TIME-MM ':' W-COMPILED-TIME-SS
PERFORM VARYING FC-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FC-DX > FORMAT-CITY-CNT
PERFORM VARYING FSN-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FSN-DX > FORMAT-STREET-NAME-CNT
PERFORM VARYING FSA-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FSA-DX > FORMAT-STREET-ADDR-CNT

PERFORM VARYING FA-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FA-DX > FORMAT-ADDRESS-CNT
ADD FORMAT-ADDRESS-WEIGHT ( FA-DX ) TO FORMAT-ADDRESS-WEIGHT-TOT
